### More details behind motivation..
The reason I ask is just that a generic `Router` implementation could be a useful standardised component, with uses outside of just asp.net core website - for example, in an `Xamarin.Forms` app it could be used to implement a navigation service that can route to an appropriate handler which could be provided by a miriad of MVVM frameworks out there.

